## Naming Conventions

| Contexto | PadrГЈo | Exemplo |
|---|---|---|
| Componentes | PascalCase | `TodayWorkoutCard` |
| Hooks | camelCase com `use` | `useDebounce` |
| FunГ§Гµes/variГЎveis | camelCase | `getGreeting` |
| Interfaces/Types | PascalCase | `WorkoutData` |
| Arquivos de componente | PascalCase | `Button/index.tsx` |
| Mock/dados locais | SCREAMING_SNAKE | `MOCK_WEEK_DAYS` |

